						/ qui non exact&egrave; sapit
						in animo, corpore, fortuna rectificanda.
					</marginalia_text>
				</position>
			</language>
			<translation>He who does not understand exactly to control mind, body, and fortune, is foolish.</translation>
		</marginalia>
